description: Travel straight down the alleyway with a brick wall on the right and a fence on the left. Turn left at the end of the alley onto the main road, then proceed through the traffic circle, passing the large 'Domain' building. Continue straight ahead; the destination 'Jumbo Jumbo Cafe' will be on the left.
